entries.name: Application
entries.description: Rollup app instance constract, responsible for holding assets and allowing the DApp to interact with other smart contracts.

entries.name: DaveConsensus
entries.description: Contract that manages PRT fraud-proof tournaments, managing application epochs and input validation, as well as settlement and challenge periods.

entries.name: MultiLevelTournamentFactory
entries.description: Contract that instantiates a PRT fraud-proof tournament, triggered every epoch.

entries.name: InputBox
entries.description: Contract that receives arbitrary blobs as inputs to Cartesi DApps.

entries.name: ERC20Portal
entries.description: Contract that allows anyone to perform transfers of ERC-20 tokens to Cartesi DApps.
